@ulope I think I know why the transactions ended up deploying more contracts than you expected.

Take a look at the [`pyethapp.rpc_client.deploy_solidity_contract() function`](https://github.com/ethereum/pyethapp/blob/develop/pyethapp/rpc_client.py#L240). It seems to scan the dependencies of the contract and also deploy them.

